Subject: [PATCH 034/194] hack! ASoC: qdsp6: Add voice call functionality in Q6
 Voice driver

q6voice combines the 3 q6voice-related services (q6mvm, q6cvp, q6cvs)
and allows to start/end voice calls at the moment.

[David]
 - replaced kzalloc with kzalloc_obj

